name: Collision leaves giant Jupiter bruised
description:
This Hubble picture, taken on 23 July, is the first full-disc, natural-colour image of Jupiter made with Hubble's new camera, the Wide Field Camera 3 (WFC3).

Name:	Jupiter
Type:	Solar System : Planet : Type : Gas Giant
Category:	Solar System
